Package: dwqInsights
Type: Package
Title: Tools for water quality sample planning and analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Elise","Hinman",email="ehinman@utah.gov", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package allows DWQ staff to explore water quality data
    used in IR assessments, delisting analyses, and TMDL development. It
    is designed to work with EPA's Water Quality Portal and DWQ's wqTools
    and irTools outputs to improve user knowledge of the state and data
    collected therein.
